    {
      "description": "Sum of llm.token_count.total per step interval, grouped by model. Use 'sum' rather than 'sum_rate' because SigNoz's sum_rate operator generates malformed SQL on dynamic (non-column) numeric attributes. Convert to a cost externally by multiplying by your provider's per-1k-token rate.",
